    Log of means between two samples

    logofMeans.between.A.B.Rd

    Computes the mean of each sample, fold change, and log fold change.

    logofMeans.between.A.B(dat, A.samples, B.samples)

    Arguments

    dat

    a dataframe. Differential analysis results from "DESeqCalculation"

    A.samples

    First sample type

    B.samples

    Second sample type

    Value

    log2 fold change of means between two given samples

    Examples

    dat <- matrix(rnorm(600, sd = 0.3), ncol = 6)
dat <- as.data.frame(dat)
logofMeans.between.A.B(dat = dat, A.samples = 1:3, B.samples = 4:6)
